<br>
I have the epic pet, 61, 62, and 65 pets and all I ever use in xp groups is the 61 pet. The 62 pet actually has better dps but without the stuns it doesnt matter in BoT and HoH and even in PoV. The amount these pets stun makes the healers have to heal less and the mobs die faster, its a lot easier to chain pull. While soloing and duoing where pet would be tanking the air pet is still the best in all tier 1 and tier 2 pop zones. The stuns are invaluable. Even though the earth has a ton of HP the healer is constantly healing it. I tested it out same mobs same healer and me with all 4 of those pets tanking and the air conserved the healers mana more than any others, all because the stuns land constantly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mevlar1>Mevlar1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 56<br> <font color=#333333>(2/16/03 8:36:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=161.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Fire pets</span><hr size=1> If the damn thing wouldn't root maybe I could use it in group situations as a stunner,  I pull up a fire pet, have it root the mob, the mob turns and eats the rogue. =/<br>
